00:43:54,610 --> 00:43:57,730
this situation often in my medical practice.

842
00:44:00,410 --> 00:44:01,570
I can imagine.

843
00:44:02,720 --> 00:44:05,360
A doctor fights against fate.

844
00:44:06,130 --> 00:44:08,170
Everyone has their own persistence.

